Mexican Drug War: 49 dismembered bodies are discovered by Mexican authorities on Mexican Federal Highway 40. The decapitated and mutilated bodies were dumped on a roadside near the northern city of Monterrey, presumably by members of the powerful Los Zetas drug cartel. (CNN) (BBC)Activists say four students are killed in an attack on anti-government demonstrations at Aleppo University, Syria. (Al Jazeera)